book:
  PMB: Administrator Guide


    July 14 2006



This guide describes the administrative functions of PMB, a free
      and opensource ILS (Integrated Library Management System, using a
      PHP/MySQL interface.


For more information, refer to www.sigb.net


    PMB version of this guide: v2.2.


      2004-2006

